  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.775048052731414         21.0901           486.35          2034.89
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.476662723558193        -12.9707          -299.11         -1251.48
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.191827624712584         -5.2199          -120.37          -503.64
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.058610179074400          1.5949            36.78           153.88
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.032237597336408         -0.8772           -20.23           -84.64
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.132930286198628          3.6172            83.42           349.01
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

